com.microsoft.azure.management.keyvault

Interface AccessPolicy.UpdateDefinitionStages.WithAttach<ParentT>

  • Type Parameters:
    ParentT - the return type of Attachable.InUpdate.attach()
    All Superinterfaces:
    AccessPolicy.UpdateDefinitionStages.WithPermissions<ParentT>, Attachable.InDefinition<ParentT>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AccessPolicy.UpdateDefinition<ParentT>
    Enclosing interface:
    AccessPolicy.UpdateDefinitionStages

    public static interface AccessPolicy.UpdateDefinitionStages.WithAttach<ParentT>
extends Attachable.InDefinition<ParentT>, AccessPolicy.UpdateDefinitionStages.WithPermissions<ParentT>
    The final stage of the access policy definition.

    At this stage, more permissions can be added or application ID can be specified, or the access policy definition can be attached to the parent key vault update using Attachable.InUpdate.attach().
